body_html: @giuliohome : The TensorFlow maintainers do not maintain or support the C#/F# bindings and have no plans of doing so. However, we happily point you to TensorFlowSharp, which is built on top of the supported C API. Any questions/comments/concerns you have there are better raised in the TensorFlowSharp repository.

body: @giuliohome : The TensorFlow maintainers do not maintain or support the C#/F# bindings and have no plans of doing so. However, we happily point you to [TensorFlowSharp](https://github.com/migueldeicaza/TensorFlowSharp), which is built on top of the supported C API. Any questions/comments/concerns you have there are better raised in the TensorFlowSharp repository.
